Door shelves are thoughtfully designed to fit gallon sized beverages and containers of varying heights.  Transparent crisper vegetable and fruit bins are humidity controlled to maximize freshness.  This unit's Multi Air Flow Cooling system chills air space consistently reaching even the furthest corners so that temperatures are constant throughout.
